- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes an algorithm to solve a problem in AI, specifically in reinforcement learning. 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems): The paper involves multiple agents (players) interacting with each other to achieve a common goal. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a decentralized algorithm for a system of multiple agents, which falls under the scope of systems and control.
